The Alliance in Artificial Intelligence brings together leading research centers


47

00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:10,600

and technology companies in Russia in order to develop their competencies


48

00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:13,120

and accelerated implementation of artificial intelligence


49

00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:17,680

in education, research and practical business activities.


50

00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:22,080

The main task of the Alliance is to provide technological


51

