Academic integrity requires acting ethically and responsibly in the learning process.


115

00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,440

and preparation of scientific texts.


116

00:07:56,440 --> 00:08:01,160

It should be remembered that the use of artificial intelligence tools for plagiarism


117

00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:06,560

Forgery, cheating in exams or research will not be tolerated.


118

00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:10,640

Using large language models provides a convenient mechanism


119

00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:13,320

for working with large amounts of information.


120

00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,680

But it is worth emphasizing that the use


121

